     | Interest Receivable | 0.00 | 2023-12-31 | 5758.38 | 2024-01-30 |

   - This indicates that there was no interest receivable at the beginning of the period (2023-12-31), and by the end of the period (2024-01-30), the amount accrued is 5758.38.

3. **Formatting the Answer**:
   - We need to structure our findings according to the specified JSON format.

Hence, based on the calculations and findings, the final output will be as follows:

{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '5758.38'}}
